OL,5, More people will be eligible for a     
OL,6, pardon for historical criminal         
OL,7, convictions relating to homosexual     
OL,8, activity, the government has said.     
OL,10,FIt means anyone convicted or cautioned 
OL,11,Ffor consensual homosexual activity,    
OL,12,Funder now-abolished laws, can apply to 
OL,13,Fhave them "disregarded".               
OL,15,FThe convictions would be wiped from    
OL,16,Frecord and an automatic pardon given.  
OL,18,FThe home secretary said she hoped the  
OL,19,Frevised scheme "would go some way to   
OL,20,Frighting the wrongs of the past".      
